Capture traffic to Virtual IP and real server same time 
tcpdump -vnni 0.0:nnnp -s 0 host x.x.vip.x and host x.x.x.x -w /var/tmp/traffic_to_vip.pcap

Normal packet capture:
#
tcpdump -s 0 -ni 0.0 -vv -w /var/tmp/09282016_fixedpos_outside_0943 port 443

Extended packet capture:
#
tcpdump -envi 0.0:nnnp -s0 'host 86.84.48.17 and port 443' -w /var/tmp/F5_ts.pcap